This project is a Power BI dashboard built using Uber Auto ride data to analyse booking performance, revenue trends, ride behaviour, and customer insights.

The goal of this dashboard is to transform raw ride data into clear, actionable insights that help understand:
Ride demand patterns
Revenue performance
Pickup & drop hotspots
Distance and booking efficiency
Customer & driver satisfaction

ğŸ¯ Objectives
The dashboard was created to:
Track total completed and lost bookings
Analyse revenue trends over time
Identify top pickup and drop locations
Measure total and average ride distance
Monitor customer and driver ratings
Compare performance using month and quarter filters

